### Admin enrols a guide in a module
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/enrolments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "guideId": "{{userId}}",
  "moduleId": "{{moduleId}}"
}

###

### Guide self-enrolls in a published module
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/enrolments/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{guideToken}}

{
  "moduleId": "{{moduleId}}"
}

###

### List enrolments (admin sees all, guide sees own)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/enrolments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update due date on an enrolment (admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/enrolments/{{enrolmentId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "dueAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z"
}

###

### Remove an enrolment (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/enrolments/{{enrolmentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
